<li><a href="/wiki/Banka_Island_massacre" title="Banka Island massacre">Banka Island massacre</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bataan_Death_March" title="Bataan Death March">Bataan Death March</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Burma_Railway" title="Burma Railway">Burma Railway</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Changjiao_massacre" title="Changjiao massacre">Changjiao massacre</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Changteh_chemical_weapon_attack" title="Changteh chemical weapon attack" class="mw-redirect">Changteh chemical weapon attack</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Comfort_women" title="Comfort women">Comfort women</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Hell_ship" title="Hell ship">Hell ships</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kaimingye_germ_weapon_attack" title="Kaimingye germ weapon attack" class="mw-redirect">Kaimingye germ weapon attack</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kalagong_massacre" title="Kalagong massacre">Kalagong massacre</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Korea_under_Japanese_rule" title="Korea under Japanese rule">Korea under Japanese rule</a></li>
